was sifted from the leaf litter of a degraded primary forest at an altitude of 
<quantity id="F660EDC25C6CFFDBFE55FD47DB47A0C8" box="[465,544,644,666]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.73" pageId="5" pageNumber="256" unit="m" value="2730.0">2730 m</quantity>
